Topic 
Week 4: The Good, the Bad, and the Ugly of Data Viz

Learning Objectives: 
- Critique visualizations based on its purpose and use or abuse of perceptual principles.
- Suggest improvements of a visualization to enhance its effectiveness.

Vitual "Worksheets" in this file include: 
1) R Pub Exploring Geometries!
2) R Pub for "Introduction to ggplot2: Part 2 (Bars)

Solutions can be found at: 
1) https://rpubs.com/hsmalley/dv_geometries
2) https://rpubs.com/hsmalley/dv_bars
